<plot>National Obsession is a twisted story following disintegrating method actor Michael Chambers, who suffering from dissociation disorder takes refuge in his on-screen character, Johnny Dekker to escape deep seated personal demons. However, when he falls so deeply into character that he ultimately rejects all who are closest to him and threatens to loose everything, he must fight to regain his true identity. But which personality will triumph in the world of Hollywood gone mad?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?390658</url></doc>
